	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: 2016 NESDev Compo - Guidelines/Rules</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It's concluded.  Between the 3 of us the decision was made to stick to original deadline of Jan 31st.  The goal is to have an annual compo that can be relied upon to end Jan 31st each year.  If you've missed out on last year's compo, you're just in time for this year's.  There will be ample time for tweaks and polishing of entries prior to cartridge production.  Late entries are still welcome and available for inclusion on the cartridge along with any other desired work that is created outside of the compo.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


